                    </title>
                    <subjectClass code="as04_01_02_02" scheme="주제">문화&gt;사상&gt;불교사상&gt;승려(법명·법호)</subjectClass>
                </biblioData>
            </front>
            <text>
                <content>
                    <paragraph align="center">○ <index type="국명">周</index>
                        <index type="이름">圓測</index>
                    </paragraph>
                    <paragraph align="center">
                        <index type="국명">周</index>
                        <index type="이름">圓測</index>
                        , 幼明敏, 講新翻<index type="서명">唯識論</index>, 旣得時譽, 後講新<index type="서명">瑜伽論</index>, 尤得其指. 蓋二論譯畢, <index type="이름">奘公</index>私爲其弟子<index type="이름">基</index>師弘闡, 使專其美, 而<index type="이름">測</index>輒闚竊, 以先發之而破其情計, 然能以法爲樂如此. <index type="이름">天后</index>初, 詔入譯經舘, 充證義員, 出<index type="서명">大乘顯識</index>等經.</paragraph>
                </content>
            </text>
        </level3>
